    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1AbsoluteLayoutParams" kindref="compound">AbsoluteLayoutParams</ref> stores per-child layout parameters for <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1AbsoluteLayout" kindref="compound">AbsoluteLayout</ref>. </para>
